            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- bottom edge fade -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-24 bg-gradient-to-t from-white to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY: dramatic statement section -->
  <section class="relative section-spacing overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 [background-image:radial-gradient(var(--color-text-dark)_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:32px_32px] opacity-[0.04]"></div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[1400px] section-padding">
      <div class="io-grid items-center">
        <!-- Big number/visual -->
        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5 mb-10 lg:mb-0" data-reveal="left">
          <div class="relative inline-flex items-baseline">
            <span class="text-[10rem] lg:text-[14rem] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] leading-none bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-brand-orange)] via-[#FF7E47] to-[#D94E1F] bg-clip-text text-transparent" data-counter data-counter-duration="1800">9</span>
            <span class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] ml-2">segundos</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-[var(--color-text-muted)] max-w-sm">
            Es el tiempo que un visitante chino concede, de media, a un sitio extranjero traducido antes de abandonarlo.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Statement -->
        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-7" data-reveal="right">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[var(--color-brand-orange)] mb-5">Por quГғВ© importa</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[44px] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-[1.15] mb-6">
            La decisiГғВіn de mayor calado del proyecto.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed mb-5">
            Puede disponer del mejor alojamiento, escoger el framework mГғВЎs sГғВіlido y completar el registro de ICP sin contratiempo alguno. Si el contenido no alcanza al lector chino, nada de ello cuenta. La pГғВЎgina se carga en menos de un segundo y el visitante la abandona a los nueve, sencillamente porque nada de cuanto lee le concierne.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed mb-8">
            De ahГғВӯ que el contenido sea la primera decisiГғВіn que abordamos. Antes del diseГғВұo, antes del desarrollo, antes de las plantillas, dejamos consignado con precisiГғВіn quГғВ© ha de decir el sitio.
          </p>

          <!-- Order pills -->
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2.5">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-cta-bg)] text-white text-sm font-medium">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white"></span>
              Contenido
            </span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white border border-[var(--color-surface-border)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] text-sm font-medium">Arquitectura</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white border border-[var(--color-surface-border)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] text-sm font-medium">DiseГғВұo</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white border border-[var(--color-surface-border)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] text-sm font-medium">Desarrollo</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT TO WRITE: comparison cards -->
  <section id="structure" class="relative section-spacing bg-gradient-to-b from-[var(--color-surface-light)] to-white overflow-hidden">
    <span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -top-24 right-[-2rem] text-[20rem] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/[0.04] leading-none select-none pointer-events-none" data-parallax="0.15">ГҘВӯвҖ”</span>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[1400px] section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-14 lg:mb-16" data-reveal>
